extendedInfo.description: At this conference you'll learn how to deal with new regulatory issues affecting tax, compliance, accounting & auditing, and governance. In addition, you'll hear new financial management and leadership strategies as well as collaboration and fund raising ideas. Explore the broad perspective and comprehensive information you can act on immediately and position your NFP or NFP clients for growth.App Keywords : aicpa, cpa2biz, not for profit, not12, GAQC,government, NFP, tax, regulatory issues,     governance, financial management, CGMA
